  "factionRules": [
    {
      "name": "Kauyon",
      "description": "Of all the principal martial philosophies revered by the Fire caste, Kauyon is the oldest, and is greatly favoured by kill teams of XV26 Stealth Battlesuits. Roughly translated as the patient hunter, Kauyon's tenets emphasise luring the enemy into overreaching before striking at them with coordinated fury. Shas'vres who are expert in this strategy employ multiple mobile assets, layers of contingencies and delaying tactics to draw foes into ambushes or corral them into pre- prepared fire boxes. Whenever a friendly XV26 STEALTH BATTLESUIT operative is shooting an enemy operative, its ranged weapons have the Accurate X weapon rule. X is determined by that enemy operative’s location."
    },
    {
      "name": "Enemy Operative Location Accurate X",
      "description": "Within 3\" of your territory Accurate 1 Within your territory Accurate 2 Within 3\" of your drop zone Accurate 3 XV26 STEALTH BATTLESUIT"
    },
    {
      "name": "Tary",
      "description": "team to date. They combine nd – of course – near invisibility. ace, the XV26 Stealth Battlesuits ently, outmanoeuvre their nterplay capabilities, monitoring mmunications to help the entire team when threatened, or striking with d System Jam to shut down plays threaten the mission. The Lodestar sitions for the team: it transports g Beacon to afford you additional points to spend on critical ploys, and Electrochaff Launcher to deter enemy eats as you push up the killzone. am – while elite in their operative es not play like any of the Space l teams, who typically spread out on and can operate fully independently. ul utility pieces the XV26 Stealth deploy to each killzone work best ion; moving your operatives in a oordinated and compact fashion s like Electrochaff Launcher and rum Sensor Package to cover and most operatives. his defensive play necessary, since m's impact comes from deliberately nd non-reciprocal attacks, not going nsively with double-action headlong hile each operative’s ranged weapons edible damage to a single target, g them at the wrong moment will ndle your limited operative count. play with the XV26 Stealth Battlesuits, st to keep your cool. With such eaponry and mobility, it could be o push forward and strike first, but kly find yourself overwhelmed by most owever, if you wait patiently and antageous engagements, you’ll be uch greater success in your hunts. e wide array of defensive tools at your foil your opponent and draw them g the game on your terms to secure XV26"
    },
    {
